64:MTA1MzQ0MDRAcXEuY29t</p>\n", "last_modified": 1678937010, "replies": 68, "id": 924457}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 54351, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181", "stars": 8275, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 94728, "username": "rwecho", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/rwecho", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2d53/5f8a/94728_mini.png?m=1678936293", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2d53/5f8a/94728_normal.png?m=1678936293", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2d53/5f8a/94728_large.png?m=1678936293", "created": 1422588717, "last_modified": 1678936293}, "last_reply_by": "season8", "last_touched": 1678963414, "title": "Edge 右上角的 B 按钮, 还挺好用的", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/924456", "created": 1678936823, "deleted": 0, "content": "看到有帖子指出 edge 升级后在右上角有个 B 的蓝色按钮, 我刚才试了下, 发现挺好用的:\r\n\r\n1. 直接打开可以和 new Bing 进行对话 (Chat)\r\n![显示对话]( https://i.imgur.com/85TSuVa.png)\r\n\r\n2. 直接可以用它来写作 (Compose)\r\n![写作助手]( https://i.imgur.com/HPZRJC5.png)\r\n\r\n3. 直接看网站信息, 可能还会抓取网页的信息,进行分析\r\n![insights]( https://i.imgur.com/MS5DDFY.png)\r\n\r\n至于 sidebar 还没搞清楚怎么用, 看起来没啥用, 不知道 e-tree 是干啥的, 难道是蚂蚁森林?\r\n\r\n我有点希望这个功能的区域能够常驻, 然后再大一点. 不知道以后这个 B 功能能不能像 vscode 那样通过 ctrl+shift+b 来唤醒", "content_rendered": "<p>看到有帖子指出 edge 升级后在右上角有个 B 的蓝色按钮, 我刚才试了下, 发现挺好用的:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>直接打开可以和 new Bing 进行对话 (Chat)\n<img alt=\"显示对话\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/85TSuVa.png\"/></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>直接可以用它来写作 (Compose)\n<img alt=\"写作助手\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HPZRJC5.png\"/></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>直接看网站信息, 可能还会抓取网页的信息,进行分析\n<img alt=\"insights\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MS5DDFY.png\"/></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>至于 sidebar 还没搞清楚怎么用, 看起来没啥用, 不知道 e-tree 是干啥的, 难道是蚂蚁森林?</p>\n<p>我有点希望这个功能的区域能够常驻, 然后再大一点. 不知道以后这个 B 功能能不能像 vscode 那样通过 ctrl+shift+b 来唤醒</p>\n", "last_modified": 1678936823, "replies": 58, "id": 924456}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 54351, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181", "stars": 8275, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 547703, "username": "echoless", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/echoless", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ea69/9bb3/547703_mini.png?m=1677129301", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ea69/9bb3/547703_normal.png?m=1677129301", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ea69/9bb3/547703_large.png?m=1677129301", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ea69/9bb3/547703_xlarge.png?m=1677129301", "created": 1623117586, "last_modified": 1677129301}, "last_reply_by": "shiqueb", "last_touched": 1678919440, "title": "这就业市场见鬼了...", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/924468", "created": 1678938339, "deleted": 0, "content": "我之前因为一个 offer 加班 1095 没接, https://www.v2ex.com/t/918503#reply48\r\n\r\n然后, 今天发现这个职位又挂出来了, 而且是急聘.\r\n\r\n此乃见鬼之一, 工人找不到工作, 企业招不到人.\r\n\r\n还是说工人躺平了, 加班的工作不要了?\r\n\r\n\r\n再说一个, \r\n\r\n最近做了一个笔试题, 有几道题要脑子里跑 python program 写结果.\r\nif a > c : xxx : else if xxx else: if x=3 else x= 5 (题没记住)\r\n\r\n最终 x =3, 求 a 是多少.\r\n\r\n我直接写了个答案: format err, (refuse to answer) 括号部分想了想就删掉了.\r\n\r\n恶心坏了, 工作中我同事让我看代码, 我都是先让他自己 refactor 一下, 格式弄好.\r\n\r\n此乃见鬼之二\r\n\r\n跟奇葩的是我要把问答题的答案写到 excel 里面.\r\n\r\n感觉笔试就是想着法子恶心求职者的.\r\n\r\n当然了, 我也是奇葩, leetcode 原题, 我做过也没做对, 水平不够.\r\n\r\n反思一下, 我好像面试带笔试的从来没有通过过 (大部分是笔试通过, 后来面试挂), 以后让笔试的通通拒了.\r\n\r\n\r\n后记:\r\n\r\n反正也找不到工作, 大家不如弄个 chatgpt 账号, 找找 idea 写代码吧.\r\n我这几天用下来, 差不多一个人+chatgpt = 一个小型团队了.\r\n\r\n干吧,兄弟们!", "content_rendered": "<p>我之前因为一个 offer 加班 1095 没接, <a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/918503#reply48\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.v2ex.com/t/918503#reply48</a></p>\n<p>然后, 今天发现这个职位又挂出来了, 而且是急聘.</p>\n<p>此乃见鬼之一, 工人找不到工作, 企业招不到人.</p>\n<p>还是说工人躺平了, 加班的工作不要了?</p>\n<p>再说一个, </p>\n<p>最近做了一个笔试题, 有几道题要脑子里跑 python program 写结果.\nif a &gt; c : xxx : else if xxx else: if x=3 else x= 5 (题没记住)</p>\n<p>最终 x =3, 求 a 是多少.</p>\n<p>我直接写了个答案: format err, (refuse to answer) 括号部分想了想就删掉了.</p>\n<p>恶心坏了, 工作中我同事让我看代码, 我都是先让他自己 refactor 一下, 格式弄好.</p>\n<p>此乃见鬼之二</p>\n<p>跟奇葩的是我要把问答题的答案写到 excel 里面.</p>\n<p>感觉笔试就是想着法子恶心求职者的.</p>\n<p>当然了, 我也是奇葩, leetcode 原题, 我做过也没做对, 水平不够.</p>\n<p>反思一下, 我好像面试带笔试的从来没有通过过 (大部分是笔试通过, 后来面试挂), 以后让笔试的通通拒了.</p>\n<p>后记:</p>\n<p>反正也找不到工作, 大家不如弄个 chatgpt 账号, 找找 idea 写代码吧.\n我这几天用下来, 差不多一个人+chatgpt = 一个小型团队了.</p>\n<p>干吧,兄弟们!</p>\n", "last_modified": 1678938339, "replies": 58, "id": 924468}]